Package: nicheCore
Title: Core Infrastructure for the Niche Ecosystem
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Niche Team", email = "niche@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides the shared foundation for the niche ecosystem, including
    standardized S3 classes (niche_spec, niche_recipe, niche_result), validation
    logic, deterministic helpers, and output conventions. This package defines
    the canonical structure and behavior that all niche packages must respect.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/nicheverse/nicheCore
BugReports: https://github.com/nicheverse/nicheCore/issues
